
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I go to Page 09 of Thoracic CT
Then 'Dynamic findings' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Dynamic findings' checkbox
Then 'Bronchial carcinoma' radio button is enabled
And 'Pleural mesothelioma' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Bronchial carcinoma' radio button
Then 'T Stage' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'N Stage' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pleural mesothelioma' radio button 
Then 'T Stage' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'N Stage' dropdown menu is enabled
